title: Number of active physicians in Alabama 2019 , by specialty area
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Number of physicians for 10 number of Specialty areas.
The Number of physicians is highest at Specialty area Total specialty and lowest at Specialty area Endocrinology diabetes & metabolism.
The difference of Number of physicians between the highest and lowest Specialty area is 6271.0.
